<h2 class="underline-light">
  <b>Disclosures</b>
</h2>
<br>
<h3>
  <b>Legal disclosures</b>
</h3>
<div class="cool-infobox">
  {{fa-icon "exclamation-circle" size="2x" prefix="fal" pull="left"}}
  <span>
    This information will not appear on your supplier profile and is not available to buyers.
  </span>
  <div class="clear-both"></div>
</div>
<p>
  You must update this information if there is change in your business that affects your answers. We will also ask you annually to update your responses to this section.
</p>
<p>
  <b>If you answer ‘yes’ to any question, you will not be disqualified, however our team may contact you to request more information.</b>
</p>
<hr class="light">
<p>
  <b>
    Is your organisation in receivership, administration or unable to meet its debts as they fall due?
  </b>
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/radio-group
    items=(array
      (hash
        key="true"
        label="Yes"
      )
      (hash
        key="false"
        label="No"
      )
    )
    field=(mut form.receivership)
    showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
    invalid=(v-get form 'receivership' 'isInvalid')
    errorMessage=(v-get form 'receivership' 'message')
    apiError=form.apiErrors.receivership
  }}
</p>
{{#if (eq form.receivership 'true')}}
  <p>
    <b>
      Please provide details
    </b>
  </p>
  <p>
    Include specific dates, details of the event and what counter measures you have implemented.
  </p>
  <p>
    {{dds/text-area
      field=(mut form.receivership_details)
      maxLength=1000
      showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
      invalid=(v-get form 'receivership_details' 'isInvalid')
      errorMessage=(v-get form 'receivership_details' 'message')
      apiError=form.apiErrors.receivership_details
    }}
  </p>
{{/if}}
<hr class="light">
<p>
  <b>
    Are any of your organisation’s directors or principals currently considered a discharged bankrupt?
  </b>
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/radio-group
    items=(array
      (hash
        key="true"
        label="Yes"
      )
      (hash
        key="false"
        label="No"
      )
    )
    field=(mut form.bankruptcy)
    showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
    invalid=(v-get form 'bankruptcy' 'isInvalid')
    errorMessage=(v-get form 'bankruptcy' 'message')
    apiError=form.apiErrors.bankruptcy
  }}
</p>
{{#if (eq form.bankruptcy 'true')}}
  <p>
    <b>
      Please provide details
    </b>
  </p>
  <p>
  Include specific dates, details of the legal action or procedure, and the outcomes.
  </p>
  <p>
    {{dds/text-area
      field=(mut form.bankruptcy_details)
      maxLength=1000
      showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
      invalid=(v-get form 'bankruptcy_details' 'isInvalid')
      errorMessage=(v-get form 'bankruptcy_details' 'message')
      apiError=form.apiErrors.bankruptcy_details
    }}
  </p>
{{/if}}
<hr class="light">
<p>
  <b>Has your organisation — or any of its directors or principals — been referred to or investigated by any agency, authority or regulator in connection with improper business practices in the last 5 years?</b>
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/radio-group
    items=(array
      (hash
        key="true"
        label="Yes"
      )
      (hash
        key="false"
        label="No"
      )
    )
    field=(mut form.investigations)
    showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
    invalid=(v-get form 'investigations' 'isInvalid')
    errorMessage=(v-get form 'investigations' 'message')
    apiError=form.apiErrors.investigations
  }}
</p>
{{#if (eq form.investigations 'true')}}
  <p>
    <b>
      Please provide details
    </b>
  </p>
  <p>
    Include specific dates, details of the event and what counter measures you have implemented.
  </p>
  <p>
    {{dds/text-area
      field=(mut form.investigations_details)
      maxLength=1000
      showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
      invalid=(v-get form 'investigations_details' 'isInvalid')
      errorMessage=(v-get form 'investigations_details' 'message')
      apiError=form.apiErrors.investigations_details
    }}
  </p>
{{/if}}
<hr class="light">
<p>
  <b>
    Has your organisation been involved in any action or procedure in a court of law in the last 5 years?
  </b>
</p>
<p>
  {{dds/radio-group
    items=(array
      (hash
        key="true"
        label="Yes"
      )
      (hash
        key="false"
        label="No"
      )
    )
    field=(mut form.legal_proceedings)
    showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
    invalid=(v-get form 'legal_proceedings' 'isInvalid')
    errorMessage=(v-get form 'legal_proceedings' 'message')
    apiError=form.apiErrors.legal_proceedings
  }}
</p>
{{#if (eq form.legal_proceedings 'true')}}
  <p>
    <b>
      Please provide details
    </b>
  </p>
  <p>
  Include specific dates, details of the legal action or procedure, and the outcome, as well as what counter measures have been implemented.
  </p>
  <p>
    {{dds/text-area
      field=(mut form.legal_proceedings_details)
      maxLength=1000
      showError=(or showError (not-eq form.status 'todo'))
      invalid=(v-get form 'legal_proceedings_details' 'isInvalid')
      errorMessage=(v-get form 'legal_proceedings_details' 'message')
      apiError=form.apiErrors.legal_proceedings_details
    }}
  </p>
{{/if}}
<p>
  {{dds/top-link}}
</p>
<hr class="light">
